General.Name: Great Tree Pharmacy Co Ltd
General.Description: Great Tree Pharmacy Co., Ltd. trades in drugs, health supplements, maternity and infant products, and cosmetics products in Taiwan. It also provides procurement services for medicines in clinics, joint outpatient centers, and cluster medical communities, as well as acts as an agent for various health care products. In addition, the company engages in the wholesale and retail, food packaging and warehousing, management consultancy, and real estate transactions activities; development, sale, and lease of industrial plants, and residential and building properties; wholesale and retail business of groceries, daily necessities, and cleaning products; trading of animal medicine, ornamental fish, and pet food. The company was formerly known as Tianjin Pharmaceutical Co., Ltd. and changed its products to Great Tree Pharmacy Co., Ltd. Great Tree Pharmacy Co., Ltd. was founded in 2001 and is based in Taoyuan City, Taiwan.
